---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout title="Home" description="wART Radio – Community radio from Marshall, NC. Listen live, check our program schedule, and support local radio.">
	<section class="hero">
		<div class="container">
			<img src="/images/hero-caboose.jpg" alt="wART Radio caboose studio" class="hero-image" width="800" height="600" />
			<h1>Welcome to wART Radio</h1>
			<p>Community radio from Marshall, NC. We're rebuilding after the flood of September 2024—and still broadcasting from our temporary home.</p>
		</div>
	</section>

	<section class="container">
		<div class="listen-live">
			<h2>Listen Live – Anytime, Anywhere</h2>
			<a href="http://station.voscast.com/5530050e0a38b/" class="listen-btn" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">
				Open stream in new tab
			</a>
		</div>

		<div class="app-links">
			<a href="https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=com.nobexinc.wls_4425973405.rc" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Download Android App</a>
			<a href="https://itunes.apple.com/us/app/wart-fm-955/id1483025647?mt=8" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Download iOS App</a>
		</div>

		<div class="card">
			<h2>Our Story</h2>
			<p>We were located in downtown Marshall, broadcasting from a little red caboose at the end of town—possibly the only radio station in a caboose. The French Broad River flowed just behind us.</p>
			<p>On September 27, 2024, the river rose some 26 feet. The flood smashed into our caboose and sent it hundreds of feet down the street. Marshall was hit hard, but our spirit wasn't. We're now operating from our temporary home at CHC/Reclaim Madison and continuing to bring you local community radio.</p>

			<h3>Watch our story</h3>
			<div class="video-wrapper">
				<video controls width="100%" playsinline preload="metadata">
					<source src="https://video.wixstatic.com/video/9c02b1_e4114a2c6d0a442280943be8ff7301c9/1080p/mp4/file.mp4" type="video/mp4" />
					<p>Your browser does not support the video. <a href="https://video.wixstatic.com/video/9c02b1_e4114a2c6d0a442280943be8ff7301c9/1080p/mp4/file.mp4" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Download the video</a>.</p>
				</video>
			</div>

			<h3>Photos after the flood of 9/27/2024</h3>
			<div class="image-gallery">
				<a href="/images/caboose-flood.jpg" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer"><img src="/images/caboose-flood.jpg" alt="Caboose in the flood" width="400" height="213" /></a>
				<a href="/images/trying-caboose.jpeg" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer"><img src="/images/trying-caboose.jpeg" alt="Trying to get into the caboose" width="400" height="298" /></a>
				<a href="/images/turntable.jpg" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer"><img src="/images/turntable.jpg" alt="Turntable" width="300" height="400" /></a>
				<a href="/images/recovered-equipment.jpg" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer"><img src="/images/recovered-equipment.jpg" alt="Recovered equipment" width="300" height="436" /></a>
			</div>

			<h3>Temporary home at CHC/Reclaim Madison</h3>
			<div class="image-gallery">
				<a href="/images/chad-jim-temp.jpg" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer"><img src="/images/chad-jim-temp.jpg" alt="Chad and Jim in the temporary location" width="400" height="300" /></a>
				<a href="/images/temp-location-2.jpg" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer"><img src="/images/temp-location-2.jpg" alt="Temporary studio" width="400" height="300" /></a>
			</div>

			<h3>Before the flood of 9/27/2024</h3>
			<div class="image-gallery">
				<a href="/images/pre-flood-1.jpg" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer"><img src="/images/pre-flood-1.jpg" alt="Caboose before the flood" width="400" height="266" /></a>
				<a href="/images/pre-flood-2.jpg" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer"><img src="/images/pre-flood-2.jpg" alt="Studio before the flood" width="400" height="266" /></a>
				<a href="/images/pre-flood-3.jpg" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer"><img src="/images/pre-flood-3.jpg" alt="wART Radio before the flood" width="400" height="266" /></a>
			</div>
		</div>

		<div class="donate-cta">
			<h3>Support wART Radio</h3>
			<p>Help us rebuild. Your donation supports our challenge grant and keeps community radio alive in Madison County.</p>
			<a href="https://www.paypal.com/donate" class="btn" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Donate with PayPal – Challenge Grant</a>
		</div>

		<div class="card">
			<h2>Check out these sites, too</h2>
